data.description: Welcome to the desirable 55+ community of, Wyndham Rose! This single-story floorplan is conveniently located nearby, Apple Valley Town Center, retail stores and, Ashwood Golf course, which makes for great daily living. This 2 bedroom / 2 bath comes with front and backyard fully landscaped for low maintenance, and is ready to be enjoyed quietly alone, or great to entertain when friends and family visit. Primary bedroom has a connected spacious bathroom, with an easy access stand-up shower, and a walk-in closet. In addition, the 2-car garage comes with cabinets to provide additional storage areas, while maintaining the garage availability for parking your vehicle(s). Come see it before it's gone! (Buyer to verify all information to buyer's satisfaction.)
